{
    "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
    "$id": "./custom_act/IfElseAction.schema.json",
    "if": {
        "properties": {
            "custom_action": {
                "const": "IfElseAction"
            }
        },
        "required": [
            "custom_action"
        ]
    },
    "then": {
        "properties": {
            "custom_action_param": {
                "$ref": "#/definitions/IfElseParam",
                "description": "IfElseAction 条件分支动作器参数\n\n根据前序识别结果的 detail.hit_node 字段分支执行：\n- hit_node=\"if\"       → 执行 if 分支\n- hit_node=\"elif[0]\"  → 执行 elif[0] 分支\n- hit_node=\"elif[1]\"  → 执行 elif[1] 分支\n- hit_node=\"else\"     → 执行 else 分支\n\n对象格式（带 next）：\n{\n    \"if\": {\n        \"Act_or_node\": [{\"action\": \"Click\", \"param\": {\"target\": true}}],\n        \"next\": [\"NextStep1\"]\n    },\n    \"elif\": [\"ActionB\", \"ActionC\"],\n    \"else\": [\"ActionD\"]\n}\n\n简写格式（无 next）：\n{\n    \"if\": [{\"action\": \"Click\", \"param\": {\"target\": true}}],\n    \"elif\": [\"ActionB\", \"ActionC\"],\n    \"else\": [\"ActionD\"]\n}\n\n字段说明：\n- if: hit_node=\"if\" 时执行的分支，可省略\n- elif: hit_node=\"elif[index]\" 时执行的分支列表，可省略。每个元素对应一个分支\n- else: hit_node=\"else\" 时执行的分支，可省略\n\n分支格式：\n- 数组: 分支项列表，无 next\n- 对象: {Act_or_node: [...], next: [...]}   \n  - Act_or_node: 分支项列表\n  - next: 分支执行完毕后依次执行的 Pipeline 节点列表\n\n分支项格式：\n- 字符串: Pipeline 节点名，通过 context.run_task() 执行\n- 字典: {\"action\": \"操作类型\", \"param\": {操作参数}}，通过 context.run_action_direct() 执行\n  action 可选值: DoNothing, Click, LongPress, Swipe, MultiSwipe, TouchDown, TouchMove, TouchUp, ClickKey, LongPressKey, KeyDown, KeyUp, InputText, StartApp, StopApp, StopTask, Scroll, Command, Shell, Screencap, Custom"
            }
        },
        "required": [
            "custom_action_param"
        ]
    },
    "definitions": {
        "IfElseParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
                "if": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/BranchDef",
                    "description": "hit_node=\"if\" 时执行的分支。可省略，省略则不执行任何操作"
                },
                "elif": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "$ref": "#/definitions/BranchDef"
                    },
                    "description": "hit_node=\"elif[index]\" 时执行的分支列表。每个元素对应一个 elif 分支，与 IfElseReco 的 elif 参数一一对应。可省略"
                },
                "else": {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/BranchDef",
                    "description": "hit_node=\"else\" 时执行的分支。可省略，省略则不执行任何操作"
                }
            },
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "BranchDef": {
            "oneOf": [
                {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "$ref": "#/definitions/BranchItem"
                    },
                    "description": "分支项列表（简写格式，无 next）"
                },
                {
                    "type": "object",
                    "description": "分支定义（对象格式，带 next）\n\n字段：\n- Act_or_node: 分支项列表\n- next: 分支执行完毕后依次执行的 Pipeline 节点列表\n\n示例：\n{\"Act_or_node\": [{\"action\": \"Click\", \"param\": {\"target\": true}}], \"next\": [\"NextStep\"]}",
                    "properties": {
                        "Act_or_node": {
                            "type": "array",
                            "items": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/BranchItem"
                            },
                            "description": "分支项列表"
                        },
                        "next": {
                            "oneOf": [
                                {
                                    "type": "string"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "array",
                                    "items": {
                                        "type": "string"
                                    }
                                }
                            ],
                            "description": "分支执行完毕后依次执行的 Pipeline 节点列表。支持单个节点名（字符串）或节点列表（数组）"
                        }
                    },
                    "additionalProperties": false
                }
            ]
        },
        "BranchItem": {
            "oneOf": [
                {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Pipeline 节点名，通过 context.run_task() 执行"
                },
                {
                    "$ref": "#/definitions/ActionDef"
                }
            ]
        },
        "ActionDef": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "直接操作定义，通过 context.run_action_direct() 执行\n\n示例：\n{\"action\": \"Click\", \"param\": {\"target\": true}}\n{\"action\": \"Swipe\", \"param\": {\"begin\": true, \"end\": [true], \"duration\": [200]}}\n{\"action\": \"ClickKey\", \"param\": {\"key\": [65]}}\n{\"action\": \"Custom\", \"param\": {\"custom_action\": \"MyAction\", \"custom_action_param\": {}}}",
            "properties": {
                "action": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "enum": [
                        "DoNothing",
                        "Click",
                        "LongPress",
                        "Swipe",
                        "MultiSwipe",
                        "TouchDown",
                        "TouchMove",
                        "TouchUp",
                        "ClickKey",
                        "LongPressKey",
                        "KeyDown",
                        "KeyUp",
                        "InputText",
                        "StartApp",
                        "StopApp",
                        "StopTask",
                        "Scroll",
                        "Command",
                        "Shell",
                        "Screencap",
                        "Custom"
                    ],
                    "description": "操作类型，对应 JActionType 枚举值"
                },
                "param": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "description": "操作参数，与 Pipeline JSON 中 action 参数格式一致。不同 action 类型对应不同参数字段"
                }
            },
            "required": [
                "action"
            ],
            "additionalProperties": false,
            "allOf": [
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "Click"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/ClickParam"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "LongPress"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/LongPressParam"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "Swipe"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/SwipeParam"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "ClickKey"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/ClickKeyParam"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "param"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "LongPressKey"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/LongPressKeyParam"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "param"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "InputText"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/InputTextParam"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "param"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "StartApp"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/StartAppParam"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "param"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "StopApp"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/StopAppParam"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "param"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "Scroll"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/ScrollParam"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                },
                {
                    "if": {
                        "properties": {
                            "action": {
                                "const": "Custom"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "action"
                        ]
                    },
                    "then": {
                        "properties": {
                            "param": {
                                "$ref": "#/definitions/CustomActionParam"
                            }
                        },
                        "required": [
                            "param"
                        ]
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
        "ClickParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "Click 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- target: 点击目标，true 表示点击识别区域中心（默认），或 [x, y, w, h] 坐标\n- target_offset: 目标偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]\n- contact: 触控点编号（多指触控），默认 0\n- pressure: 按压力度，默认 1\n\n示例：\n{\"target\": true}\n{\"target\": [100, 200, 50, 50], \"target_offset\": [0, 0, 0, 0]}",
            "properties": {
                "target": {
                    "description": "点击目标，true 表示点击识别区域中心"
                },
                "target_offset": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "default": [0, 0, 0, 0],
                    "description": "目标偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]"
                },
                "contact": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 0,
                    "minimum": 0,
                    "description": "触控点编号（多指触控），默认 0"
                },
                "pressure": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 1,
                    "minimum": 0,
                    "description": "按压力度，默认 1"
                }
            },
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "LongPressParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "LongPress 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- target: 长按目标，true 表示识别区域中心（默认）\n- target_offset: 目标偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]\n- duration: 长按时长（毫秒），默认 1000\n- contact: 触控点编号，默认 0\n- pressure: 按压力度，默认 1\n\n示例：\n{\"target\": true, \"duration\": 2000}",
            "properties": {
                "target": {
                    "description": "长按目标，true 表示识别区域中心"
                },
                "target_offset": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "default": [0, 0, 0, 0],
                    "description": "目标偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]"
                },
                "duration": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 1000,
                    "minimum": 0,
                    "description": "长按时长（毫秒），默认 1000"
                },
                "contact": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 0,
                    "minimum": 0,
                    "description": "触控点编号，默认 0"
                },
                "pressure": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 1,
                    "minimum": 0,
                    "description": "按压力度，默认 1"
                }
            },
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "SwipeParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "Swipe 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- begin: 起始位置，true 表示识别区域中心（默认）\n- begin_offset: 起始偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]\n- end: 终点位置列表，[true] 表示识别区域中心（默认）\n- end_offset: 终点偏移列表，默认 [[0, 0, 0, 0]]\n- end_hold: 终点停留时间列表（毫秒），默认 [0]\n- duration: 滑动时长列表（毫秒），默认 [200]\n- only_hover: 是否仅悬停，默认 false\n- contact: 触控点编号，默认 0\n- pressure: 按压力度，默认 1\n\n示例：\n{\"begin\": true, \"end\": [true], \"duration\": [500]}",
            "properties": {
                "starting": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 0,
                    "minimum": 0,
                    "description": "MultiSwipe 中使用，默认 0"
                },
                "begin": {
                    "description": "起始位置，true 表示识别区域中心",
                    "default": true
                },
                "begin_offset": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "default": [0, 0, 0, 0],
                    "description": "起始偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]"
                },
                "end": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "description": "终点位置列表，[true] 表示识别区域中心",
                    "default": [true]
                },
                "end_offset": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "description": "终点偏移列表，默认 [[0, 0, 0, 0]]",
                    "default": [[0, 0, 0, 0]]
                },
                "end_hold": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "default": [0],
                    "description": "终点停留时间列表（毫秒），默认 [0]"
                },
                "duration": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "default": [200],
                    "description": "滑动时长列表（毫秒），默认 [200]"
                },
                "only_hover": {
                    "type": "boolean",
                    "default": false,
                    "description": "是否仅悬停，默认 false"
                },
                "contact": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 0,
                    "minimum": 0,
                    "description": "触控点编号，默认 0"
                },
                "pressure": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 1,
                    "minimum": 0,
                    "description": "按压力度，默认 1"
                }
            },
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "ClickKeyParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "ClickKey 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- key: 按键代码列表（必填），如 [65] 表示 A 键\n\n示例：\n{\"key\": [65]}",
            "properties": {
                "key": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "description": "按键代码列表（必填），如 [65] 表示 A 键"
                }
            },
            "required": ["key"],
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "LongPressKeyParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "LongPressKey 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- key: 按键代码列表（必填）\n- duration: 长按时长（毫秒），默认 1000\n\n示例：\n{\"key\": [65], \"duration\": 2000}",
            "properties": {
                "key": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "description": "按键代码列表（必填）"
                },
                "duration": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 1000,
                    "minimum": 0,
                    "description": "长按时长（毫秒），默认 1000"
                }
            },
            "required": ["key"],
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "InputTextParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "InputText 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- input_text: 输入文本（必填）\n\n示例：\n{\"input_text\": \"Hello\"}",
            "properties": {
                "input_text": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "输入文本（必填）"
                }
            },
            "required": ["input_text"],
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "StartAppParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "StartApp 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- package: 应用包名（必填）\n\n示例：\n{\"package\": \"com.example.app\"}",
            "properties": {
                "package": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "应用包名（必填）"
                }
            },
            "required": ["package"],
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "StopAppParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "StopApp 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- package: 应用包名（必填）\n\n示例：\n{\"package\": \"com.example.app\"}",
            "properties": {
                "package": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "应用包名（必填）"
                }
            },
            "required": ["package"],
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "ScrollParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "Scroll 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- target: 滚动目标，true 表示识别区域中心（默认）\n- target_offset: 目标偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]\n- dx: 水平滚动距离，默认 0\n- dy: 垂直滚动距离，默认 0\n\n示例：\n{\"target\": true, \"dy\": 100}",
            "properties": {
                "target": {
                    "description": "滚动目标，true 表示识别区域中心",
                    "default": true
                },
                "target_offset": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "default": [0, 0, 0, 0],
                    "description": "目标偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]"
                },
                "dx": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 0,
                    "description": "水平滚动距离，默认 0"
                },
                "dy": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "default": 0,
                    "description": "垂直滚动距离，默认 0"
                }
            },
            "additionalProperties": false
        },
        "CustomActionParam": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "Custom 操作参数\n\n字段：\n- custom_action: 自定义动作名（必填）\n- target: 目标，true 表示识别区域中心（默认）\n- custom_action_param: 自定义动作参数\n- target_offset: 目标偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]\n\n示例：\n{\"custom_action\": \"MyAction\", \"custom_action_param\": {}}",
            "properties": {
                "custom_action": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "自定义动作名（必填）"
                },
                "target": {
                    "description": "目标，true 表示识别区域中心",
                    "default": true
                },
                "custom_action_param": {
                    "description": "自定义动作参数"
                },
                "target_offset": {
                    "type": "array",
                    "items": {
                        "type": "integer"
                    },
                    "default": [0, 0, 0, 0],
                    "description": "目标偏移 [x, y, w, h]，默认 [0, 0, 0, 0]"
                }
            },
            "required": ["custom_action"],
            "additionalProperties": false
        }
    }
}
